title: House Heals: LA Fire Benefit
description:
Presenting HOUSE HEALS: A House music + visual art fundraiser at The Midway

This Sunday 2-8PM we are throwing the biggest fundraiser event for The LA fire effort, with 100% of ticket proceeds going to Pasadena Humane and California Fire Foundation — one organization doing life saving work for 300+ animals in the last 48 hours and the other directly helping both the brave men and women fighting the fires and the victims.

With a lineup of Bay Area artists, both DJ and visual, we all want to come together to raise money for our friends and fam to the South and show them we are standing with them.
